
filmload v1.0.1

This script loads a film from YouTube.com, Ok.ru, Vk.com, Mail.ru,
Rutube.ru and Brighteon.com by the url to the output filename,
selecting an optimal video format (neither very large, nor very small)
for watching on a tv screen.

This script uses programs for loading videos:

  - curl
  - youtube-dl
  - yt-dlp

So, these programs should be installed in your operating system.
